  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Emergency sanitation and hygiene promotion for South Sudan refugees in Palorinya settlement &#x2013; Moyo district</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The main objective is to strengthen emergency sanitation and hygiene service delivery to 30,000 South Sudan refugees and host community in Palorinya settlement &#x2013; Moyo district. The targeted communities will be provided with materials, necessary toolkit, information and training to enable them innovatively  construct household latrines and basic home sanitation facilities; and household latrines for persons with special needs will be constructed by established youth groups. The project will be implemented over 9 months.</narrative>
  </description>
